      <title>暴雨导致法国小麦产量跌至四年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-sees-wheat-harvest-plunging-to-4-year-low-on-heavy-rains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧洲最大农业生产国法国降雨过多，影响了农作物的产量前景，法国软小麦产量预计将跌至 2020 年同期的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/france-sees-wheat-harvest-plunging-to-4-year-low-on-heavy-rains</guid>
