      <title>肯尼亚随区域协议生效开始征收进口关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/kenya-begins-levying-import-duties-as-regional-deal-kicks-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为区域协议的一部分，肯尼亚开始对从尿布到豌豆等所有商品征收进口关税，但该协议并未受到总统威廉·鲁托放弃提高国内税计划的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/kenya-begins-levying-import-duties-as-regional-deal-kicks-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 08:22:54 GMT</pubDate>
